name: Fictophilia
description: I'm kind of guy, who lives in the fictional world, ofcourse in my imaginations. So, recently watched an anime series, there, I saw a girl and at first sight, I fell in her love. She was the most beautiful thing that I had ever seen and I wanted her with me. But it was impossible. So I took the advantage of my art skills and drew myself with her. That's why, I named this artwork "Fictophilia". Here, We are in love with each other
